{"meta":{"title":"Morôni 4","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/4?lang=por","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ//2013-06-255-moroni-04-64k-por.mp3","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"727b1bc3cfd1fddd1db72f0f1eca5eb29dbf1822","data-aid":"124208428","data-aid-version":"3","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/4","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"por","data-orig-id":"3e1ae322e4eeed3898d379132f1dd2011137ebbd","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"Morôni 4","description":"Explica-se como élderes e sacerdotes administram o pão sacramental. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"Morôni 4","description":"Explica-se como élderes e sacerdotes administram o pão sacramental. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124208815\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 4</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124208816\" id=\"study_summary1\">Explica-se como élderes e sacerdotes administram o pão sacramental. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124208817\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span><a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>Maneira</a> pela qual seus <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>élderes</a> e sacerdotes administravam a carne e o sangue de Cristo à igreja; e eles <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>administravam-nos</a> de acordo com os mandamentos de Cristo. Sabemos, portanto, que esta maneira é correta; e o élder ou o sacerdote ministrava-os —</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124208818\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>E ajoelhavam-se com a igreja e oravam ao Pai, em nome de Cristo, dizendo:</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124209819\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Ó Deus, Pai Eterno, nós te rogamos em nome de teu Filho, Jesus Cristo, que abençoes e santifiques este <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>pão</a> para as almas de todos os que partilharem dele, para que o comam em <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>lembrança</a> do corpo de teu Filho e testifiquem a ti, ó Deus, Pai Eterno, que desejam tomar sobre si o <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>nome</a> de teu Filho e recordá-lo sempre e guardar os mandamentos que ele lhes deu, para que possam ter sempre consigo o seu <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3d\"><sup class=\"marker\">d</sup>Espírito</a>. Amém.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"4\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124209822\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.1-7?lang=por#p1\">3 Né. 18:1–7</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note1b\" data-full-marker=\"1b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124209824\" id=\"note1b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/elder?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Élder (Ancião)</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note1c\" data-full-marker=\"1c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124209828\" id=\"note1c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.76-77?lang=por#p76\">D&amp;C 20:76–77</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124209831\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/sacrament?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Sacramento</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note3b\" data-full-marker=\"3b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124209197\" id=\"note3b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/luke/22.19?lang=por#p19\">Lc. 22:19</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/1-cor/11.23-24?lang=por#p23\">1 Cor. 11:23–24</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.7?lang=por#p7\">3 Né. 18:7</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note3c\" data-full-marker=\"3c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124209198\" id=\"note3c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/jesus-christ?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Jesus Cristo — Tomar sobre nós o nome de Jesus Cristo</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"d\" id=\"note3d\" data-full-marker=\"3d\">\n<p data-aid=\"124209200\" id=\"note3d_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/holy-ghost?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Espírito Santo</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","associated":{"title_number1":[{"sizes":"250px","alt":"A Bênção do Sacramento","aspectRatio":"0.6666666666666666","height":"480","width":"320","missingAsset":"false","assetId":"4032b9ebee7fc0b2e3dceb8d519ed720f47b5e06","srcset":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/d0/d9/d0d9d491433fd36c464db2234b33da3478b2f549/deacons_sacrament_paraguay.jpeg 60w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/cd/ec/cdec282a86aa0b605707dd8b33b49600d821e2b0/deacons_sacrament_paraguay.jpeg 100w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/fc/08/fc083c35b6d44a5496a3430fcc9ff19a9f9f5524/deacons_sacrament_paraguay.jpeg 200w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/eb/4a/eb4a797a541105b3afccacd362682bd817d37ca3/deacons_sacrament_paraguay.jpeg 250w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/e4/73/e473d3a4a7c8c6c58960de50138be1b6ca15217e/deacons_sacrament_paraguay.jpeg 320w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/63/49/6349cdd96037e